Introduction
This program is a shopping application.
When you run the project, you will be in the Login menu, you can type "help" command
to see all commands available in this menu.
this program supports 3 role, 1- admin, 2- seller, 3- buyer, you can choose any of them to 
create account and each of them has some special ability.
Admin can see other users, products and categories and aslo can create new categories.
Each Product have a category.
